24
00:01:50,750 --> 00:01:51,269
Sure.

25
00:01:51,270 --> 00:01:52,520
Let's add each other on WeChat.

26
00:01:54,950 --> 00:01:57,430
(Flirting everywhere he goes.)

27
00:01:57,550 --> 00:01:58,630
Here.

28
00:01:59,030 --> 00:02:00,510
Scan this.

29
00:02:02,710 --> 00:02:03,550
Yan Lidong.

30
00:02:03,870 --> 00:02:05,029
Come here, I need the script.

31
00:02:05,030 --> 00:02:05,829
Thanks.

32
00:02:05,830 --> 00:02:07,550
Isn't the script on your desk?

33
00:02:08,790 --> 00:02:09,750
I...

34
00:02:10,190 --> 00:02:12,510
Hold it for me. I need to read it!

35
00:02:14,510 --> 00:02:16,390
Let's add WeChat first.

36
00:02:19,790 --> 00:02:20,950
Let's go.

37
00:02:21,790 --> 00:02:22,749
Hey handsome.

38
00:02:22,750 --> 00:02:24,070
Interested in debuting?

39
00:02:25,270 --> 00:02:26,589
Director, bad news.

40
00:02:26,590 --> 00:02:26,949
Zhu Yi...

41
00:02:26,950 --> 00:02:28,670
Zhu Yi got into a minor car accident.

42
00:02:29,750 --> 00:02:31,920
Why did this have to happen
at such a critical moment?

43
00:02:32,470 --> 00:02:33,909
The second male lead has a big role.

44
00:02:33,910 --> 00:02:35,389
If we cast someone last-minute,

45
00:02:35,390 --> 00:02:36,950
we won't have enough time.

46
00:02:38,870 --> 00:02:39,830
This...

47
00:02:42,670 --> 00:02:44,109
Mu Chenxi's assistant.

48
00:02:44,110 --> 00:02:45,150
Let him try.

49
00:02:45,430 --> 00:02:47,229
Chen... Chenxi!

50
00:02:47,230 --> 00:02:49,189
Mr. Yan just got dragged into acting!

51
00:02:49,190 --> 00:02:50,389
If the chairman finds out,

52
00:02:50,390 --> 00:02:51,789
we're doomed.

53
00:02:51,790 --> 00:02:52,909
When did this happen?

54
00:02:52,910 --> 00:02:54,190
Just now.

55
00:03:05,950 --> 00:03:07,190
Your Highness.

56
00:03:08,750 --> 00:03:09,990
Princess.

57
00:03:16,190 --> 00:03:17,030
Your Highness.

58
00:03:17,630 --> 00:03:18,670
Your Highness.

59
00:03:19,350 --> 00:03:21,110
Why are you so foolish?

60
00:03:21,190 --> 00:03:23,030
Because I promised you

61
00:03:23,470 --> 00:03:25,270
I would always protect you.

62
00:03:29,190 --> 00:03:31,190
(Acting with Yan Lidong)

63
00:03:31,470 --> 00:03:33,110
(isn't so bad.)

64
00:03:41,590 --> 00:03:42,910
Third Prince.

65
00:03:42,950 --> 00:03:44,790
Wan'er, why are you here?

66
00:03:45,350 --> 00:03:47,269
I heard you're leaving for battle today.

67
00:03:47,270 --> 00:03:48,670
I came to see you off.

68
00:03:49,110 --> 00:03:50,429
This is a protection charm

69
00:03:50,430 --> 00:03:52,390
I got for you at Huguo Temple.

70
00:03:53,750 --> 00:03:55,750
Then I'll keep it with me every day.

71
00:03:59,910 --> 00:04:02,230
It's cold outside. Go back now.

72
00:04:02,550 --> 00:04:03,709
They look so good together.

73
00:04:03,710 --> 00:04:05,030
Yeah, they do.

74
00:04:06,150 --> 00:04:07,470
What are you doing?

75
00:04:09,630 --> 00:04:11,309
What did you promise me?

76
00:04:11,310 --> 00:04:13,110
I told you to stay away
from the Third Prince.

77
00:04:13,470 --> 00:04:15,230
Yet here you are, giving him a charm.

78
00:04:15,390 --> 00:04:17,230
That desperate for his attention?

79
00:04:22,310 --> 00:04:23,749
Whatever he can give you,

80
00:04:23,750 --> 00:04:25,150
I can too.

81
00:04:39,270 --> 00:04:40,549
Don't think I don't know

82
00:04:40,550 --> 00:04:42,390
who you really are.

83
00:04:46,070 --> 00:04:46,830
Cut.

84
00:04:47,310 --> 00:04:48,590
Great performance.

85
00:04:52,950 --> 00:04:54,110
Chenxi.

86
00:04:54,790 --> 00:04:56,789
A new restaurant just opened nearby.

87
00:04:56,790 --> 00:04:58,470
Want to grab a bite together?

88
00:04:58,590 --> 00:05:00,349
Sure, I'm actually a bit hungry.

89
00:05:00,350 --> 00:05:01,469
Let's go now.

90
00:05:01,470 --> 00:05:02,430
Mm.

91
00:05:11,910 --> 00:05:13,389
You go do your thing.

92
00:05:13,390 --> 00:05:15,870
We're having a private dinner.

93
00:05:17,350 --> 00:05:18,350
Let's go.

94
00:05:33,710 --> 00:05:35,310
It's been so many years.

95
00:05:35,430 --> 00:05:36,349
I still think

96
