about our college days.

97
00:05:42,550 --> 00:05:43,389
Look.

98
00:05:43,390 --> 00:05:44,870
This character is written so...

99
00:05:51,430 --> 00:05:52,990
Back then,

100
00:05:53,750 --> 00:05:54,910
