101
00:05:55,870 --> 00:05:57,310
What's so great about him?

102
00:05:57,510 --> 00:05:58,589
Isn't he just an overhyped

103
00:05:58,590 --> 00:05:59,470
celebrity?

104
00:06:00,030 --> 00:06:02,109
