105
00:06:02,110 --> 00:06:04,070
Do you actually believe that nonsense?

106
00:06:08,790 --> 00:06:10,670
I haven't kept in touch for so long,

107
00:06:10,710 --> 00:06:12,390
I feel like I missed out on a lot.

108
00:06:12,630 --> 00:06:14,750
It's all in the past.

109
00:06:14,990 --> 00:06:16,790
I ordered your favorite steak.

110
00:06:16,830 --> 00:06:17,870
Try it.

111
00:06:48,550 --> 00:06:49,670
Not good.

112
00:06:53,990 --> 00:06:55,110
This one's pretty good.

113
00:06:56,470 --> 00:06:57,830
What are you doing here?

114
00:06:58,030 --> 00:06:59,670
I'm here to test for poison.

115
00:07:00,830 --> 00:07:01,790
This one's safe.

116
00:07:04,150 --> 00:07:05,229
Chenxi.

117
00:07:05,230 --> 00:07:05,629
Mm?

118
