I'm starving.

132
00:08:16,550 --> 00:08:18,429
(CEO or not,)

133
00:08:18,430 --> 00:08:21,150
(in the end, he still listens to me.)

134
00:08:23,190 --> 00:08:24,390
Here, your meal.

135
00:08:27,230 --> 00:08:28,390
I'll eat.

136
00:08:28,910 --> 00:08:31,070
Eat up. Keep testing for poison.

137
00:08:40,790 --> 00:08:42,590
I can't eat anymore.

138
00:08:44,710 --> 00:08:46,030
You're full?

139
00:08:54,510 --> 00:08:55,630
